马卡龙在[[韩国|韩国]]十分流行。<ref>Cha, Daniella: [http://phoenixplume.com/2011/04/macarons-the-new-trend-for-desserts/ "Macarons: The New Trend for Desserts."] Phoenix Plume. The official newspaper for Korea International School, 27 April 2011. Retrieved 8 December 2012.</ref> 它在[[朝鮮語|韩语]]中被叫做"ma-ka-rong"（마카롱）。[[抹茶|绿茶粉]]或[[綠茶|綠茶]]可以被用来制作绿茶马卡龙。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.naver.com/PostView.nhn?blogId=baby0817&logNo=40135718804|script-title=ko:마카롱,마카롱만드는법|date=7 August 2011|publisher=Naver|language=ko|accessdate=8 May 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064030/http://blog.naver.com/PostView.nhn?blogId=baby0817&logNo=40135718804|archive-date=2016-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gracefulcuisine.com/green-tea-french-macaron-recipe/|title=Green tea French macaron recipe|author=Dr. Grace|date=17 March 2012|publisher=Graceful Cuisine|accessdate=8 May 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150802055705/http://www.gracefulcuisine.com/green-tea-french-macaron-recipe/|archive-date=2015-08-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===日本===
马卡龙在[[日本|日本]]被叫做 "makaron"（マカロン），<ref>{{cite web|url=http://fukuishimbun.co.jp/fu/plaza_blog/blog/2010/07/09/%E3%82%B8%E3%83%A3%E3%83%B3%E3%83%95%E3%82%A3%E3%83%AA%E3%83%83%E3%83%97%E3%83%BB%E3%83%80%E3%83%AB%E3%82%B7%E3%83%BC%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%8F%E3%81%AE%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%9C%E3%83%9E%E3%82%AB%E3%83%AD%E3%83%B3/|script-title=ja:|date=9 July 2010|title=ジャン=フィリップ・ダルシー「夏の新作マカロン」|publisher=福井新聞社| language=ja|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120317114444/http://fukuishimbun.co.jp/fu/plaza_blog/blog/2010/07/09/%E3%82%B8%E3%83%A3%E3%83%B3%E3%83%95%E3%82%A3%E3%83%AA%E3%83%83%E3%83%97%E3%83%BB%E3%83%80%E3%83%AB%E3%82%B7%E3%83%BC%E3%80%8C%E5%A4%8F%E3%81%AE%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%9C%E3%83%9E%E3%82%AB%E3%83%AD%E3%83%B3/|archivedate=2012-03-17}}</ref> 也是一种流行的糕点。有一种版本也叫马卡龙，但是用花生粉代替了杏仁粉，是[[和菓子|和菓子]]口味的，在日本广泛流行。

===臺灣===
法國馬卡龍名店Ladurée曾入駐臺灣，引發一股精致甜點馬卡龍的風潮<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/345975 |title=為何馬卡龍界的LV在台開幕三年就黯然撤點？她一語道破法國百年老店無法深耕台灣之因… |access-date=2019-01-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114210706/https://www.storm.mg/lifestyle/345975 |archive-date=2019-01-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。台北馬卡龍名店單價在50~138元。

臺灣本土自創的西式糕點[[牛粒|牛粒]]，或稱「小西點」，因牛粒外型與法國馬卡龍相似，在法國馬卡龍引進台灣後，而被稱作「臺式馬卡龍」，但牛粒與馬卡龍做法與口味截然不同。<ref>{{cite web |author1=朱宥勳 |title=朱宥勳：法式甜點在台灣的秘密，比你想像的還要多 |url=https://theinitium.com/article/20160428-culture-food-frenchdessertintaiwan/ |website=端傳媒 |publisher=端傳媒科技（香港）有限公司 |accessdate=2021-05-19 |archive-date=2021-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210519035015/https://theinitium.com/article/20160428-culture-food-frenchdessertintaiwan/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==流行程度==
在巴黎，[[拉杜麗|拉杜麗]]连锁糕点店因为它的马卡龙而闻名于世长达{{As of|2009|alt=150年}}。<ref name="WSJ1">{{cite news|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704269004575073843836895952.html|title=Mon Dieu! Will Newfound Popularity Spoil the Dainty Macaron?|publisher=The Wall Street Journal|date=March 2, 2010|accessdate=December 29, 2010|first=Julie|last=Jargon|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304173448/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704269004575073843836895952.html|archive-date=2010-03-04|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYTimes1">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/02/01/nyregion/westchester/01qbitewe.html|title=Macaroon Delight|publisher=The New York Times|date=January 29, 2009|accessdate=December 29, 2010|first=M. H.|last=Reed|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130112022835/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/02/01/nyregion/westchester/01qbitewe.html|archive-date=2013-01-12|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在法国，[[麦当劳|麦当劳]]在他们的[[McCafé|McCafé]]咖啡馆里销售马卡龙（有时使用把马卡龙的形状比做成汉堡形状的广告）。 <ref name="WSJ1" /> McCafé的马卡龙由{{le|Château Blanc|Château Blanc}}生产，就像拉杜丽一样，是{{le|Groupe Holder|Groupe Holder}}集团的子公司，尽管他们采用不同的马卡龙配方。<ref name="WSJ1" />

欧洲以外的地方，法式马卡龙还可见于[[加拿大|加拿大]]和美国。<ref name="Canada.com1">{{cite news|last1=Chesterman|first1=Lesley|url=http://www.canada.com/cityguides/montreal/story.html?id=5b194459-45fd-45bf-8adf-218af1e3aa40|title=Macaron mania hits Montreal - finally!|publisher=The Gazette (Montreal)|date=October 11, 2008|accessdate=December 29, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109203926/http://www.canada.com/cityguides/montreal/story.html?id=5b194459-45fd-45bf-8adf-218af1e3aa40|archivedate=2012年11月9日}}</ref><ref name="SeattleTimes1">{{cite news | url=http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/pacificnw/2010071487_pacificptaste25.html | work=The Seattle Times | first=Rebekah | last=Denn | title=French macarons are sweet, light and luscious | date=October 25, 2009 | access-date=2015-07-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111011074509/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/pacificnw/2010071487_pacificptaste25.html | archive-date=2011-10-11 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="LATimes1">{{cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2010/apr/01/food/la-fo-macaron-20100401|title=Macarons: New to The Easter Parade This Year|publisher=Los Angeles Times|date=April 1, 2010|accessdate=December 29, 2010|first=Dorie|last=Greenspan|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120102155032/http://articles.latimes.com/2010/apr/01/food/la-fo-macaron-20100401|archive-date=2012-01-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NPR1">{{cite news|url=http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=123566536|title=Move Over, Cupcake: Make Way For The Macaroon|publisher=NPR|date=February 12, 2010|accessdate=December 29, 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150808134847/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=123566536|archive-date=2015-08-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="eggzmacaron1">{{cite news | url=http://www.eggzmacaron.com | work=Il est difficile de résister à atteindre pour un autre! | title=eggzmacaron | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801104359/http://eggzmacaron.com/ | archivedate=2015-08-01 }}</ref>

在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]，{{le|Adriano Zumbo|Adriano Zumbo}}连同电视剧《[[我要做廚神_澳洲版|我要做廚神]]》，一同见证了马卡龙如何成为了一道广受欢迎的甜品，它现在被麦当劳放在McCafe的出口处销售。<ref>{{cite web|last=Chavassieu|first=Olivia|title=Heaven on Earth|url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/good-living/heaven-on-earth/2008/04/14/1208025069622.html|publisher=Sydney Morning Herald|accessdate=7 March 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924200747/http://www.smh.com.au/news/good-living/heaven-on-earth/2008/04/14/1208025069622.html|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>

3月20日是全球的“马卡龙日”。2005由[[皮埃尔·艾尔梅|皮埃尔·艾尔梅]]糕点坊在巴黎创设了这一节日，并作为一个传统而传遍世界。在这一天，世界上参与节日活动的面包店和马卡龙门店向顾客提供一份免费的马卡龙样品。马卡龙所有额外销售的百分之一将被捐献给当地的慈善组织<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mymacaronrecipe.com/macaron-day-2013/ |title=Macaron Day 2013 |access-date=2015-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619025206/http://www.mymacaronrecipe.com/macaron-day-2013/ |archive-date=2015-06-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；但可能有部分地區的「馬卡龍日」不與全球同步，比如[[日本|日本]]的6月21日<ref>{{cite web|url=http://empowerproject.jp/archives/453|title=明日、6/21は「マカロンデー」です|date=2018年6月20日|accessdate=2018年7月22日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180722095843/http://empowerproject.jp/archives/453|archive-date=2018年7月22日|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

